# Walkthrough - Email Personalization & Preview

I have added powerful personalization features to your cold email outreach. Now, you can use placeholders like `{Business_Name}` to make every email feel custom-made for the lead.

## New Features

### 1. Placeholder Support
You can now use the following tags in your email templates (both in the AI-generated ones and your custom campaigns):
- `{Business_Name}`: The name of the company.
- `{Location}`: The city or address of the business.
- `{Website}`: The URL of their current website.
- `{Phone}`: Their business phone number.
- `{Service}`: The type of service they offer (e.g., "restaurant", "café", "photography").

Here's the full breakdown with the `{Service}` value you'd plug in for each category:

